---
title: Chesapeake Cheddar Burgers with Potato Wedges & Old Bay® Aioli
description: In this extra-savory spin on burger night, spicy Old Bay seasoning and savory Worcestershire sauce add oomph to beef patties. Griddle to perfection, add cheddar slices, then tuck them into golden toasted brioche buns spread with what we call “Old Bay-oli”—that’s mayo, mustard, garlic, and Old Bay! Serve with seasoned potato wedges on the side.
